Body:
self.ad.setup(quantity='pore.blah', conductance='throat.foo',
    diffusive_conductance='throat.foo2', hydraulic_conductance=
    'throat.foo3', pressure='pore.bar')
assert self.ad.settings['quantity'] == 'pore.blah'
assert self.ad.settings['conductance'] == 'throat.foo'
assert self.ad.settings['diffusive_conductance'] == 'throat.foo2'
assert self.ad.settings['hydraulic_conductance'] == 'throat.foo3'
assert self.ad.settings['pressure'] == 'pore.bar'
self.ad.setup(quantity='pore.concentration', conductance=
    'throat.ad_dif_conductance', diffusive_conductance=
    'throat.diffusive_conductance', hydraulic_conductance=
    'throat.hydraulic_conductance', pressure='pore.pressure')
